creator: Givvy
descriptionHtml:
What if you could enjoy the benefits of sports betting without actually losing money? What if you could predict matches and compete with your friends who have bet better results?
Predict the outcome of the match on each half time and the final results and number of goals without actually losing your money.
You can easily follow up on your odds, join private leagues and beat your friends as well without investing your money. Watch stats and other player’s predictions. What’s better than that? You can win the Jackpot in the leaderboard by proving you are the best!
If you are a football lover, likes to bet on the number of goals or the correct outcome then we got you covered.
Download now, bet and enjoy the matches!
